is like creating many secrets together.

00:19:42.814 --> 00:19:47.519
{\an8}I guess the two of us
aren't just friends anymore.

00:19:49.521 --> 00:19:50.856
{\an8}What? Mom?

00:19:50.923 --> 00:19:53.158
{\an8}I like any version of you.

