{\an8}Hold on.

00:19:57.963 --> 00:19:58.864
{\an8}I can't.

00:19:58.931 --> 00:20:01.900
{\an8}Only insecure men get jealous.

00:20:01.967 --> 00:20:03.402
{\an8}I'm taking Haruka back.

